.</p></div></a><a class=\"park-card-premium-link\" href=\"/parks/priority-chicago-lakeview-loft\"><div class=\"park-card-standard \"><div class=\"park-premium-header\"><h3 class=\"park-premium-title\">Lakeview Loft Play Lab</h3><div class=\"park-header-group\"><div class=\"status-pill closed\">unknown</div><div class=\"park-premium-rating\"><i class=\"bi bi-star\"></i><span>5</span></div></div></div><div class=\"park-status-note\">Hours vary by season</div><div class=\"park-premium-location\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i><span>Chicago<!-- -->, <!-- -->IL</span></div><div class=\"park-premium-badges\"><span class=\"premium-badge type-badge\">INDOOR</span><span class=\"premium-badge price-badge\">$$</span></div><p class=\"park-premium-description\">Second-story loft with rubberized agility floors, scent work workshops, and rooftop relief turf for Lakeview and Lincoln Park condo dwellers.</p></div></a></div></div></div></section><section id=\"nearby-cities\" class=\"nearby-cities-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"section-heading\"><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Explore the region</span><h2>Dog parks near <!-- -->Chicago</h2><p>Worth the drive? Check out top-rated indoor parks in neighboring cities.</p></div><div class=\"nearby-cities-grid\" style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));gap:1.5rem;margin-top:2rem\"><a class=\"nearby-city-card\" style=\"display:block;text-decoration:none;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;background:white;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;transition:transform 0.2s\" href=\"/cities/naperville\"><div class=\"nearby-city-image\" style=\"position:relative;height:180px;background-color:#f1f5f9\"><img alt=\"Dog parks in Naperville, IL\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:cover;color:transparent\" src=\"/images/cities/naperville/hero.webp\"/></div><div class=\"nearby-city-content\" style=\"