ors in Chicago?\\\",\\\"acceptedAnswer\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Answer\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"Yes. Our directory currently lists 4 indoor dog parks in Chicago. Use the “Indoor Dog Park” filter on this page to jump straight to climate-controlled options.\\\"}},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Question\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"How do indoor dog park prices work in Chicago?\\\",\\\"acceptedAnswer\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Answer\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"Expect $15–$25 weekday drop-ins, $35–$45 weekend peak sessions, and $95+ monthly memberships that bundle agility classes or coworking desks. Premium lounges add bar tabs or locker rentals.\\\"}},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Question\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Are memberships worth it for downtown apartment dogs?\\\",\\\"acceptedAnswer\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Answer\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"Yes—unlimited play tiers guarantee predictable schedules, guest passes, and priority access to private suites when the lakefront freezes. Most plans include two human passes so roommates or sitters can check in.\\\"}},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Question\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Can I host a cowork-and-play session at Chicago indoor parks?\\\",\\\"acceptedAnswer\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Answer\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"Spaces like Paws \\u0026 Co. Lounge provide sound-proof phone booths, sit-stand desks, and concierge dog attendants so you can work from the park. Book weekday blocks online and bring proof of vaccinations and insurance if you are a vendor.\\\"}}]}\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"26:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"script\\\",null,{\\\"type\\\":\\\"application/ld+json\\\",\\\"suppressHydrationWarning\\\":true,\\\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\\\":{\\\"__html\\\":\\\"$2e\\\"}}]\\n27:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"script\\\",null,{\\\"type\\\":\\\"application/ld+json\\\",\\\"suppressHydrationWarning\\\":true,\\\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\\\":{\\\"__html\\\":\\\"{\\\\\\\"@context\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"https://schema.org\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"@type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"BreadcrumbList\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"itemListElement\\\\\\\":[{\\\\\\\"@type